# Competency question: "Which narrative time axes exist, and is the
# fabula/syuzhet space spanned with no privileged winner?"
# Expected: exactly purrdf:axisDiscourseTime (syuzhet — the order of telling)
# and purrdf:axisStoryTime (fabula — the order of happening in-universe).
# The chapter sequence is the syuzhet projection of frame-relative story
# content (#359, EPIC #358); neither axis is the truth of the other.

PREFIX purrdf: <https://blackcatinformatics.ca/purrdf/>

SELECT ?axis WHERE {
    ?axis a purrdf:NarrativeTimeAxis .
}
ORDER BY ?axis
